Update here: I have taken a look.  The scripts work OK, but do not pass our test suite for a number of reasons.  The PS scripts here are written the way that the old batch scripts were: they have all of the activation logic in the script, none in Conda.  The new scripts change that, so that Conda does things like figuring out where to look for environments.

I am adapting the PS scripts as I have time.

